<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267225>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Leptalpheus pereirai sp. nov., holotype, male (cl 7.2 mm), from Bocas del Toro, Panama (MZUSP 34067): a, frontal region, dorsal view; b, same, lateral view; c, sixth pleomere, lateral view; d, telson, dorsal view; e, tooth on ventromesial carina of first article of antennular peduncle, lateral view; f, proximal portion of antennular flagella, lateral view; g, third maxilliped, lateral view; h, appendices masculina and interna of second pleopod, mesial view; i, uropod, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267225/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267226>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Leptalpheus pereirai sp. nov., holotype, male (cl 7.2 mm), from Bocas del Toro, Panama (MZUSP 34067): a, major (right) cheliped, lateral view; b, same, mesial view; c, same, chela, mesial view; d, same, chela fingers, lateral view; e, detail of tooth on cutting edge of dactylus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267226/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267227>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Leptalpheus pereirai sp. nov., holotype, male (cl 7.2 mm), from Bocas del Toro, Panama (MZUSP 34067): a, minor (left) cheliped, lateral view; b, same, chela, lateral view; c, same, chela fingers (open); d, second pereiopod, lateral view; e, third pereiopod, lateral view; f, fourth pereiopod, latreral view; g, fifth pereiopod, lateral view; h, same, distal portion of propodus and dactylus, mesial view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267227/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267228>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Leptalpheus pereirai sp. nov., holotype, male (cl 7.2 mm), from Bocas del Toro, Panama (MZUSP 34067): live shrimp in lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267228/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

